data.description: Recently renovated home on 5 ACRES with everything you could ask for! Owners have created the perfect retreat complete with a new roof, top of the line Pella windows and doors throughout, new in-ground pool, outbuildings, raised gardens, STOCKED pond, appliances including a SPEED QUEEN washing machine! A split floor plan offers privacy, and the primary has an attached office/nursery for added convenience. There is also a beautiful sunroom leading to the pool as well as a large bonus room!
